  "description": "A long-exposure nighttime shot of a harbor or bay with a large cargo ship being loaded or unloaded. The ship is illuminated with bright work lights, and large container cranes stand alongside it. A long bridge stretches across the water, adorned with a string of lights. In the background, the dark shapes of hills or low mountains can be seen against a bright orange and red sky, suggesting either a sunrise or sunset. The water reflects the light, creating a shimmering path that leads toward the ship. There are also several other smaller vessels or structures visible near the shore and along the waterway.",
